				<outline text="1/3 Blogging went through the same thing that podcasting is going through now, it was taken apart by Twitter, Facebook, Google Reader, Medium and lately Substack. You couldn't write in one place and have your writing flow to all of them, the way podcasting works today. They don't" type="tweet" created="Fri, 20 Aug 2021 14:54:00 GMT" tweetId="1428732052355100684" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1428732052355100684" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
					<outline text="2/3 agree on what a post is, so no matter what, you'd have to write at least two or three versions of a post. In the end, you just blow them all off, because it isn't worth the trouble, the resulting format is taking the fun out of your thinking and writing process. You aren't" type="tweet" created="Fri, 20 Aug 2021 14:54:01 GMT" tweetId="1428732056545148940" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1428732056545148940" inReplyToId="1428732052355100684" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
						<outline text="3/3 getting anything out of it. Not money, not exploration of ideas, not getting other people excited." type="tweet" created="Fri, 20 Aug 2021 14:54:03 GMT" tweetId="1428732064971505664" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1428732064971505664" inReplyToId="1428732056545148940" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
							<outline text="More here.. 

https://t.co/7UCqP6KCw1" type="tweet" created="Fri, 20 Aug 2021 15:03:05 GMT" tweetId="1428734339794227200" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1428734339794227200" inReplyToId="1428732064971505664" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
							</outline>
						<outline text="BTW, a hat-tip to Automattic. 

Of all the companies involved in producing blog-like things, they support most of what we think of as a subscribable site. 

Not sure how they handle titleless posts, but have the rest covered well." type="tweet" created="Fri, 20 Aug 2021 15:24:28 GMT" tweetId="1428739718301294592" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1428739718301294592" inReplyToId="1428732056545148940" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
						</outline>
					</outline>
