			<outline text="August 1" type="calendarDay" name="01" >
				<outline text="So dear @mehdirhasan — what do you propose to do about it? This rant is getting stale. You’re earning a living by saying this over and over along with the others at msnbc. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/mehdirhasan/status/1422023931368771584&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 02:43:18 GMT" tweetId="1422025182491947010" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1422025182491947010" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="Saying the Repubs are gone as a party isn’t going to get us back on track. 

There’s a big fight coming. It’d be better to have it now with a rule of law president in the White House. 

Putting off the fight is like waiting to be vaccinated until you’re about to be incubated." type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 02:37:44 GMT" tweetId="1422023785230872585" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1422023785230872585" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
					<outline text="The first thing to do is expel all the Repubs who voted to overthrow the election from Congress." type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 02:45:12 GMT" tweetId="1422025663498924033" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1422025663498924033" inReplyToId="1422023785230872585" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
