				<outline text="Lock him up. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnn.com/2021/08/01/politics/kevin-mccarthy-nancy-pelosi-gavel/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 02:14:42 GMT" tweetId="1422017986517417989" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1422017986517417989" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="The big corporate podcasts will be as vacuous and void of substance as corporate news. And the low barrier to entry will still enable nutritious ideas to be distributed. It all depends on what people want. Ideas or mindless chatter. &lt;a href=&quot;https://amp.theguardian.com/media/2021/aug/01/listen-up-why-indie-podcasts-are-in-peril?__twitter_impression=true&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 02:13:25 GMT" tweetId="1422017664843649026" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1422017664843649026" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="Making sense of conservatives’ sudden vaccine endorsements. &lt;a href=&quot;https://news.yahoo.com/making-sense-of-conservatives-sudden-vaccine-endorsements-150144023.html?ncid=dcm_23910565_301671439_473553414_136036780&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 02 Aug 2021 01:57:33 GMT" tweetId="1422013672554209282" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1422013672554209282" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
