			<outline text="July 31" type="calendarDay" name="31" >
				<outline text="Provincetown, Mass., the quirky community at the tip of Cape Cod, thought it was safe to return to prepandemic partying. It wasn’t. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/31/us/covid-outbreak-provincetown-cape-cod.html?unlocked_article_code=AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACEIPuonUktbfqohkT1UYAibIRp8sqQOHib3I3aA2nHL3L22NUzFczuIeDpSH5EGIbqN7ap442DjdRMNENPVnYs1O-dJlHh4nTRi08NzDkY4ZIi4xpMXuB21uhp7DBvVlrGO6KzS3ebg6lLHu41eLOWbsDaHZ2XEqI1t1sNAyIwHRrH8JxqrCFO&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 01 Aug 2021 00:59:11 GMT" tweetId="1421636595220992005" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1421636595220992005" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
