where is america's heart? &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1421532393899442180&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 31 Jul 2021 18:06:09 GMT" tweetId="1421532649290600454" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1421532649290600454" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
