				<outline text="In a sane America, Jordan was booted from Congress. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/mkraju/status/1417261895820656651&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 02:08:08 GMT" tweetId="1417305292145143809" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1417305292145143809" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
