					<outline text="Anyone who reads me regularly knows I fully agree with @MichaelWolffNYC. In fact, I wrote this earlier today after hearing the Joint Chiefs guy didn't prevent the insurrection he saw coming. Why does he still have his job, he's not doing his duty, same with the journos. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1417302388759793673/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 01:56:36 GMT" tweetId="1417302388759793673" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1417302388759793673" inReplyToId="1417289301084282880" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="From Macy’s to Albertsons, facial recognition is already everywhere. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vox.com/2021/7/15/22577876/macys-fight-for-the-future-facial-recognition-artificial-intelligence-stores&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 23:09:34 GMT" tweetId="1417260355823222786" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1417260355823222786" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
