				<outline text="If journalism is to thrive, the paywalls have to go away. It's the wrong user experience. It forces a question at a time when it's virtually impossible that the user is going to buy your pitch. https://t.co/kkznbda9Tb" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 00:13:30 GMT" tweetId="1416914055747579908" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1416914055747579908" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
