				<outline text="White supremacy is on the ballot until further notice. It's the only issue, believe it or not, in the US. And probably around the world too.  https://t.co/RNAaFKXzAt" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 12:20:21 GMT" tweetId="1415285035108868102" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1415285035108868102" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
