				<outline text="After all we've been through, Covid, the Insurrection, the fires and hurricanes, it amazes me how little imagination has crept into American political discourse." type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 18:57:53 GMT" tweetId="1412848361967960066" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1412848361967960066" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="after all we've been through, covid, the insurrection, it amazes me how little imagination has crept into american political discourse." type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 18:56:48 GMT" tweetId="1412848087123607558" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1412848087123607558" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="A new toolkit for OPML support. 

&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/scripting/opmlPackage&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;

Node and browser-based code to read and write OPML files. Makes it easy for outliners and tools to interop. 

We say no to silos. ❤️" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 18:51:56 GMT" tweetId="1412846863762460679" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1412846863762460679" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
					<outline text="An 18-minute podcast that explains why I did this OPML toolkit for JavaScript, now. 

https://t.co/2USUym9g9r" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 13:58:52 GMT" tweetId="1413135498055327757" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1413135498055327757" inReplyToId="1412846863762460679" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="1/2 About Trump's claim that Twitter and Facebook are obligated by the First Amendment, I'm not sure that's wrong. If a social network is so large that they effectively control all speech in a channel, if there's no way around them, different rules should apply." type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 18:41:15 GMT" tweetId="1412844175255556099" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1412844175255556099" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
					<outline text="2/2 On the other hand, speech, even as guaranteed by the government, is not an absolute. The Constitution is not a suicide pact, President Lincoln said." type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 18:41:17 GMT" tweetId="1412844183367344139" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1412844183367344139" inReplyToId="1412844175255556099" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="I was asked &quot;What is an outliner?&quot; 

An outliner is a text editor that organizes information in a hierarchy, allowing users to control the level of detail and to reorganize according to structure.

Much more here...

https://t.co/s2RAlWp8nd

