				<outline text="I did a poll, about 1/2 prefer dark mode, so I decide why not give them a choice. So I'm adding dark mode to Drummer. It's going pretty well. It's weird, feels different, makes me laugh, but I kind of like it. Still have some glitches to work out. :-) https://t.co/ca6KFpopaV" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 15:31:21 GMT" tweetId="1405186241973342212" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1405186241973342212" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
