					</outline>
				<outline text="1/4 When is journalism going to start asking when the DOJ is going to charge Trump with insurrection? They seem to be stuck, for years, reporting what everyone knows. Trump tried to use the DOJ as if it were his personal mobbed-up law firm. He didn't accept the results of the" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 14:27:59 GMT" tweetId="1405170293463785479" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1405170293463785479" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
