						<outline text="3/4 time to start asking the obvious question, we're going to stay stuck. The question, on the off chance it isn't obvious is this -- when are you going to make Trump pay for his crimes against the country? Tax evasion is cute, we want to see him pay for trying to overthrow the" type="tweet" created="Wed, 16 Jun 2021 14:28:09 GMT" tweetId="1405170335289430019" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1405170335289430019" inReplyToId="1405170314196172807" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
